messages.content:
Let me collect everything in one form. Fill in what you know — leave anything blank for me to decide:

```json
{
  "form": {
    "title": "Style Replication — Content Brief",
    "intro": "Same camera composition as the reference. Replace everything else.",
    "fields": [
      {
        "id": "model",
        "label": "Model",
        "type": "text",
        "placeholder": "e.g. Filipina woman, mid-20s, confident energy — or leave blank for me to decide"
      },
      {
        "id": "product",
        "label": "Product (replaces the basketball)",
        "type": "text",
        "placeholder": "e.g. skincare serum bottle, 50ml frosted glass — or leave blank"
      },
      {
        "id": "setting",
        "label": "Setting (replaces outdoor basketball court)",
        "type": "text",
        "placeholder": "e.g. rooftop at golden hour, beach, urban street — or leave blank"
      },
      {
        "id": "text_eyebrow",
        "label": "Eyebrow text (top — was: MOBILE EDITING CLUB)",
        "type": "text",
        "placeholder": "e.g. YOUR BRAND NAME"
      },
      {
        "id": "text_subhead",
        "label": "Subhead (was: How to use)",
        "type": "text",
        "placeholder": "e.g. Introducing"
      },
      {
        "id": "text_hero",
        "label": "Hero headline (was: Claude.)",
        "type": "text",
        "placeholder": "e.g. GlowUp."
      },
      {
        "id": "text_qualifier",
        "label": "Qualifier italic (was: for Brands)",
        "type": "text",
        "placeholder": "e.g. for your skin"
      },
      {
        "id": "text_cta",
        "label": "CTA button (was: OUR WORKFLOWS →)",
        "type": "text",
        "placeholder": "e.g. SHOP NOW →"
      },
      {
        "id": "color_grade",
        "label": "Color grade / mood",
        "type": "select",
        "options": ["Keep cool editorial (like reference)", "Warm golden tone", "Moody dark contrast", "Clean bright white", "Director decides"]
      }
    ],
    "submit_label": "Build my prompt"
  }
}
```
